usage() {
  cat <<EOF
Usage: tools/mylite-mtr-harness [list|coverage|run|probe|list-storage|run-storage|probe-storage|list-unsupported|list-unclassified] [suite.test...]

Commands:
  list           Show curated MariaDB MTR smoke tests.
  coverage       Show accepted curated MTR counts against the imported test
                 inventory without building or running MTR.
  run            Build the MTR smoke prerequisites and run exact selected tests.
                 Defaults to the curated smoke list.
  probe          Build the MTR smoke prerequisites, run exact selected tests,
                 and continue after failures. Exits nonzero if any test does
                 not report an MTR pass. Removes newly generated .reject files.
  list-storage   Show MyLite storage-routed MTR smoke tests.
  run-storage    Build the storage MTR prerequisites and run exact selected
                 storage-routed tests. Defaults to the storage smoke list.
  probe-storage  Probe exact selected tests against the storage MTR profile.
  list-unsupported
                 Show probed and selector-expanded MTR candidates kept out of
                 accepted coverage with reason categories as tab-separated
                 test, category, reason rows.
  list-unclassified
                 Show imported upstream MTR tests that are neither accepted
                 coverage nor known unsupported probes or selectors.

Environment:
  BUILD_DIR          Baseline MariaDB build directory. Defaults to build/mariadb-mtr-smoke.
  PROFILE            Baseline CMake cache. Defaults to cmake/mariadb-mtr-smoke.cmake.
  STORAGE_BUILD_DIR  Storage MariaDB build directory. Defaults to build/mariadb-mtr-storage-smoke.
  STORAGE_PROFILE    Storage CMake cache. Defaults to cmake/mariadb-mtr-storage-smoke.cmake.
  STORAGE_PRIMARY_FILE
                     Storage primary .mylite file for run-storage/probe-storage.
  STORAGE_INIT_BUILD_DIR
                     First-party build directory for mylite-storage-init. Defaults to build/dev.
  STORAGE_INIT_TOOL  Existing mylite-storage-init path to use instead of building one.
  MTR_BUILD_THREAD   MTR build thread/port block. Defaults to auto.
  MTR_PROBE_TESTCASE_TIMEOUT_MINUTES
                     Probe testcase timeout passed to MTR. Defaults to 5.
EOF
}

